      • rebatchMessage

        public static Optional<RawMessage> rebatchMessage(RawMessage msg,
                                                  BiPredicate<String,org.apache.pulsar.client.api.MessageId> filter)
                                           throws IOException
        Take a batched message and a filter, and returns a message with the only the submessages which match the filter. Returns an empty optional if no messages match. This takes ownership of the passes in message, and if the returned optional is not empty, the ownership of that message is returned also.
        抛出:
        IOException
